得遵从主流价值观才能活得更好，谁能帮我解惑一下。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4193f58a4bdc473968c36d5eaba5748c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/606491841"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+fa7xOmGpsgjEAMaCDk3MDU2Mjg2IM2/o6QGMAA4gwRAMXIJNjA2NDkxODQxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0}